# Technology Stack

## Environment Management
- Conda environment: 'vbl'
- Python version: 3.12
- Package management: pip
- Required environment variables: [None]

## Core Technologies
- Backend: Python 3.12
- ML Framework: PyTorch 2.6
- ML Libraries: Huggingface
- Frontend: HTML/JS/Gradio
- Database: MySQL
- Testing: pytest
- Linting: ruff


## Project Structure
vibe/                          # Root folder (not in git)
├── vibe_coding/               # Git repository
│   ├── src/                   # Main source code
│   │   ├── models/            # ML model implementations
│   │   │   ├── hf/            # Using Huggingface transformers
│   │   │   └── py/            # Using raw PyTorch
│   │   ├── data_loaders/      # Data loading utilities
│   │   └── utils/             # Utility functions and helpers
│   ├── notebooks/             # Jupyter notebooks for experiments
│   ├── tests/                 # Test files mirroring src structure
│   │   └── models/            # Model tests
│   ├── docs/                  # Documentation
│   ├── requirements.txt       # Python dependencies
│   ├── README.md              # Project documentation
│   └── .env                   # Environment variables (not in git)
└── vhub                       # Resource files for ML (not in git)
    ├── data/                  # Dataset files
    ├── pretrained/            # Pre-trained models
    └── checkpoints/           # Training checkpoints

## Development Guidelines
- Test coverage: Required for all model code
- Documentation: Docstrings for functions and classes
- Environment: Keep .env local, never commit
- vHub: Store outside git repository in vibe root folder